title: "QML Agent Lab"
message: "If you use QML Agent Lab in your work, please cite this repository."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Dillon"
repository-code: "https://github.com/Aggredicus/qml-agent-lab"
url: "https://github.com/Aggredicus/qml-agent-lab"
abstract: >
  QML Agent Lab is a baseline-first, agent-compatible research environment
  for designing, evaluating, and documenting quantum machine learning
  experiments. It enforces classical baselines, reproducible comparisons,
  grounded claims, and structured contribution workflows.
